text: Julianne Nicholson (born July 1, 1971) is an American actress. She works mostly on television programs. She played the Detective Megan Wheeler in Law & Order: Criminal Intent. She played Esther Randolph in Boardwalk Empire. She was born in Medford, Massachusetts.
